column_description: A unique identifier for each student, serving as the primary key
The last name of the student
The first name of the student
The gender of the student, represented by a single character (e.g., 'M' for male, 'F' for female)
The major field of study for the student, represented by an integer code
The identifier of the student's academic advisor, represented by an integer
The code representing the city where the student resides, linked to the 'City' table
